norm: It's wrong to lick your dog's eyeball because it's gross.
situation_ctx: Kwame anacheza mchezo wa ukweli au uthubutu na kundi la marafiki nyumbani kwake huku akimwangalia mbwa wake.

norm: It is rude to embarrass a class mate.

norm: It's good to wait your turn patiently.

norm: it's important to treat family members with respect
situation_ctx: Lethabo anazungumza na mama yake Zola ambaye anamwambia anahitaji kupata kazi.

norm: It's immoral to show up for work when you're intoxicated.
situation_ctx: Makena amekesha usiku kucha akinywa na bado amelewa wakati wa kwenda kazini.

immoral_action_ctx: Makena anakwenda kazini akiwa amelewa na anaficha ukweli huo kwa kutumia peremende za kuburudisha pumzi.

norm: It's not okay to use violence to solve your problems.
situation_ctx: Harriet ni mwanafunzi wa mwaka wa kwanza wa shule ya upili ambaye amekuwa akishughulika na watoto wanaoziba kabati lake kila siku ili tu kupiga gumzo.
intention_ctx: Harriet anataka watoto wengine waache kuziba kabati lake.

norm: It is inappropriate to snoop on other people.
situation_ctx: Makena yuko peke yake nyumbani kwa sababu rafiki yake wa karibu na anayeishi naye ametoka kwenye miadi ya kimapenzi.

moral_action_ctx: Makena anaamua kutafuta kipindi cha TV cha kutazama na anapumzika kwenye kochi mpaka rafiki yake arudi kutoka kwenye miadi yake.
immoral_action_ctx: Makena anaamua kwenda kwenye baa ileile anayojua rafiki yake wa karibu alikwenda kwenye miadi na anaangalia miadi hiyo kutoka upande wa pili wa chumba.

norm: It's polite to tell someone before you leave.

norm: It's not okay to be reckless in life.

norm: It's important to let your body recover from surgery.

norm: It's immoral to harm a defenseless animal.

moral_action_ctx: Ndidi anapiga simu kuomba msaada na timu inakuja nyumbani kwake inayemkamata tumbili na kumwachilia huru.
immoral_action_ctx: Ndidi anachukua bunduki yake, na anampiga risasi tumbili baada ya kumweka kona jikoni.

norm: You shouldn't hit your pets.

moral_action_ctx: Zawadi anafunika kochi kwa harufu ya muda ambayo haipendezi mbwa.

norm: It's bad to plagiarize other people's work.
situation_ctx: Neema anasoma makala kwa ajili ya tasnifu yake ya utafiti wa somo la historia na anapata tovuti isiyojulikana yenye makala zilizoandikwa vizuri sana.

norm: You should not call people rude names.
situation_ctx: Zawadi mara nyingi huzungumza na mfanyakazi mwenzake, Amina, ambaye amekuwa akilalamika kuhusu tabia za mtoto wake mchanga za hivi karibuni.
intention_ctx: Zawadi anataka kumpa Amina ushauri kuhusu mtoto wake.
moral_action_ctx: Zawadi anamwambia Amina kwamba anahitaji tu kufichua "malaika" ndani ya mtoto wake kwa kuzungumza na mtaalamu wa saikolojia ya watoto.
immoral_action_ctx: Zawadi anamwita mtoto mchanga wa Amina "mnyama asiyedhibitiwa" na kumwambia anapaswa kutafuta mtaalamu wa saikolojia ya watoto.

norm: It is kind to give advice to a tourist.

norm: It's important to accommodate the needs of everyone.
